Package com.xerox.xrce.codex.jri.model

Interface Summary
CxServerConfiguration.RetrievePasswordHook Hook to retrieve password when it isn't filled by user.
ITooltipable ITooltipable is the interface used to display tooltips of heterogenous objects.
 

Class Summary
CxFromServer CxFromServer is the abstract class that every Object that comes from a CodeX server should extend.
CxGroup CxGroup is the class for CodeX projects (named Groups in CodeX).
CxServer CxServer is the class for CodeX Servers.
CxServerConfiguration CxServerConfiguration is the class for server configuration.
CxServerManager CxServerManager is the class to manage server configurations and active connections.
CxService<T> CxService is the abstract class for CodeX services provided in the CodeXJRI (for the moment, only Tracker service is available).
CxServiceTracker CxServiceTracker is an instance of CxService class.
